SAVE A PRESET:
Type: !save my_protocol_name
Click: ➕ Add to Method
Saved in: cycle_templates.json

LOAD A PRESET:
Type: @my_protocol_name
Click: ⚡ Spark

BUILT-IN TEMPLATES:
@spark titration - Dose-response series (auto-generates 5 concentrations + regen)
@spark kinetics - Association + long dissociation + regeneration
@spark amine coupling - Full amine coupling workflow
@spark binding - Multi-concentration binding template
@spark baseline - Single baseline cycle
@spark regeneration - Single regeneration cycle

QUICK GENERATION:
build 5 - Auto-generates 5 × (Binding 15min + Regen + Baseline)
build 10 - Auto-generates 10 × (Binding 15min + Regen + Baseline)
